   Users must comply with all applicable third-party licenses. See the 
   documentation for a complete list of third-party components and their 
   licenses.

6. EXPORT RESTRICTIONS
   This software may be subject to export control laws and regulations. 
   Users are responsible for compliance with all applicable export control 
   laws and regulations in their jurisdiction.

7. NO WARRANTY FOR SPECIFIC PURPOSES
   While this software is designed for secure data destruction, it is 
   provided without warranty for any specific purpose. Users should test 
   and validate the software for their specific use cases and requirements.

8. LIMITATION OF LIABILITY
